analysis.interpretation: 3-qubit GHZ fidelity: 86.6% on Tuna-9. Significant noise with 13.4% leakage into non-GHZ states. Asymmetry between |000⟩ (48.4%) and |111⟩ (38.2%) suggests qubit-dependent error rates.

b = measure q
